title: Katherine_Dempsey
text:
Hi! My name is Katherine, and welcome to my journey of learning to code in R.


I am a 2nd year graduate student, and my current project focuses on how tumor cells reprogram stromal cell metabolism in pancreatic cancer.



Prior to starting my PhD program, I earned my Bachelor’s degree in Biomedical Chemistry from Oral Roberts University and completed a Summer Undergraduate Research Fellowship at UT Southwestern.
